        <h2> What is the SCP Foundation?</h2>
        <p>The SCP foundation is a global secret organization is responsible for locating and containing individuals, entities, locations, and objects that violate natural law (referred to as SCPs). <span class="important">WE PROTECT THE WORLD AND HUMANITY</span>.</p>
        <h2>What happens if I join the SCP Foundation?</h2>
        <p>Your existence will be erased, articals that have connections with you will be changed, no one will know you, not even a single insect and animal will know you. <span class="important">YOU WEREN'T EVEN BORNED</span>.</p>
        <h2>OK, but I'm still not convinced</h2>
